      "title": "Corona at Ragama railway station",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the Corona virus, the ticketing station of Ragama railway station is temporarily closed. It has been decided to close the ticketing station after the station master was confirmed to be infected with the coronavirus."
